Hi everyone , Does  {% if %} {% else %} works in programmable beta email modules

 I am having issue in writing a programmable beta logic in the email module. When I chose a contact having contact owner, it works fine, goes inside if statement pulls all the data. but when I chose a contact which does not contact owner, it does not goes to else statement. Any solution to this?

{% set contact_broker_email = contact.HubSpot_owner_id.email %}
{% if contact_broker_email %}
  {% set query_broker="mc_broker_email="~contact_broker_email %}
  {% set broker_ob = crm_object("broker_info", query_broker, broker_email, broker_phone,") %}
  {% set broker_email = <http://broker_ob.mc|broker_ob.mc>_broker_email %}
  {% set broker_phone = <http://broker_ob.mc|broker_ob.mc>_broker_phone %}
  {% set emailus = 'Email me' %}
{% else %}
  {% set broker_email = '<mailto:defaultemail@gmail.com|defaultemail@gmail.com>' %}
  {% set broker_phone = '1111111' %}
  {% set emailus = 'Email us' %}
{% endif %}
